OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772813483
OL,3,CBurst pipe leaves homes with no water
OL,4,Cas Thames Water warns more may lose
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FHomes in Oxford remain without water
OL,8,For are experiencing low pressure for a
OL,9,Fsecond day following a burst water
OL,10,Fmain, with Thames Water warning more
OL,11,Fpeople may be affected today.
OL,13,FA large pipe burst on a field next to
OL,14,FOxford Road on Wednesday. (4 March)
OL,16,FThames Water say engineers have worked
OL,17,Fovernight, and remain on site as of
OL,18,F8am Thursday morning and are "making
OL,19,Fprogress" with the repair.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
