PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772813483
OL,3,CBurst pipe leaves homes with no water
OL,4,Cas Thames Water warns more may lose
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FThe company said said it has been
OL,8,F"more difficult" than expected due to
OL,9,Fexcessive ground water and that a
OL,10,Fstandard clamp fix is unusable.
OL,12,FA Thames Water spokesperson said: "Our
OL,13,Fcrews have been working overnight to
OL,14,Fcarefully excavate around the damaged
OL,15,Fsection of the 800mm main.
OL,17,F"Due to the nature of the burst, a
OL,18,Fstandard clamp fix is unusable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772813483
OL,3,CBurst pipe leaves homes with no water
OL,4,Cas Thames Water warns more may lose
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"Special fittings are already under
OL,8,Ffabrication and plans underway for
OL,9,Femergency transport. A commissioning
OL,10,Fplan has been prepared to safely bring
OL,11,Fthe main back into service.
OL,13,F"We are bringing in additional staff
OL,14,Ffrom across our region to support,
OL,15,Fwith special measures in place to keep
OL,16,Fhospitals in supply.
OL,18,F"It is highly likely that further
OL,19,Fcustomers are going to experience
OL,20,Fwater outages but we are trying to
OL,21,Frebalance the network to minimise.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
