PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772813483
OL,3,CBurst pipe leaves homes with no water
OL,4,Cas Thames Water warns more may lose
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"We are very sorry for the ongoing
OL,8,Fdisruption. We fully understand how
OL,9,Finconvenient and worrying this is, and
OL,10,Fwe are working as quickly and safely
OL,11,Fas possible to resolve the issue and
OL,12,Frestore supplies."
OL,14,FThere are bottled water stations at:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
